🔉#SOUNDON: We’re going green for our #digestion 💚😍 Treat your #gut with this Garden Greens Soup! The leafy greens in it are a good source of #fiber, that can help the growth of #healthy gut #bacteria. 
Full Recipe: 
1 bunch kale (8-10 whole leaves)
3 ½ cups chicken or vegetable broth
½ bunch fresh parsley, leaves only, coarsely chopped (about 1 cup, loosely packed)
3 cups fresh spinach leaves (about 3 ounces)
2 cups broccoli florets (about 5 ounces)
1 large carrot, coarsely grated
3 green onions (both white and green parts), roughly chopped
2 large garlic cloves, roughly chopped
2 TBSP white miso paste, or to taste
Juice of half a lemon, or to taste
1/4 TSP red pepper flakes
Salt and pepper to taste
4 scoops Herbalife Nutrition Simply Probiotic

Per serving:
Calories:  160
Protein: 13 g
Carbohydrate: 27 g
Fat: 3 g
Fiber: 6.5 g
